WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.945
Insourcing is doing project with internal resources,

00:00:03.945 --> 00:00:08.130
while outsourcing is getting it done outside your company.

00:00:08.130 --> 00:00:10.065
When should you insource?

00:00:10.065 --> 00:00:13.560
When it is crucial that intellectual property, or IP,

00:00:13.560 --> 00:00:19.425
should remain in-house, when understanding of culture and project is required,

00:00:19.425 --> 00:00:24.300
when the work needed to be done aligns with your core business activities,

00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:27.930
and when a project deals with sensitive enterprise information,

00:00:27.930 --> 00:00:29.880
such as security data.

00:00:29.880 --> 00:00:35.145
You should outsource when a variety of skills are needed to complete the project.

00:00:35.145 --> 00:00:39.385
Outsourcing gives you access to larger talent pool.

00:00:39.385 --> 00:00:42.860
You should consider outsourcing when the work does not

00:00:42.860 --> 00:00:46.555
fall into the category of your core business functions.

00:00:46.555 --> 00:00:51.080
You should consider outsourcing when you need to scale quickly.

00:00:51.080 --> 00:00:55.710
Outsourcing sometimes can also be cost-effective.

